        <div class="msgSubject">Character Models are Awesome</div>
        <div class="sm notbold">
          
          Posted: 2010-11-21 14:54:02 | Edited: Nov 21 2010  2:54pm  | <input type="checkbox" name="quote-1290372842243717842" id="quote-1290372842243717842" class="msgQuoteCheck" onchange="multiQuote2()"/><label for="quote-1290372842243717842" onclick="multiQuote2()"> Quote</label>  | <a href="/forum.html?forum=152&amp;mid=1290372842243717842&amp;post=1&amp;replyto=1290372842243717842&amp;page=1" class="icon-replytothis" rel="nofollow">Reply to Post</a> | <a id="FOLLOW_MID_1290372842243717842" onclick="followToggle('add','1290372842243717842')" href="javascript:" class="icon-follow">Follow</a> 
