      <div class="msgContentFrame">The character models are indeed stunning. I like how angry, sad, happy, etc.(all the other emotes) all have a facial expression that matches. The detail on all the armors is very neat too and I can't wait to see what other gear will be headed our way in the future.  <br /> <br />Going back to the facial expressions, although a minor issue, but one that was just a tad annoying in FFXI. I disliked when in FFXI you would do /cheer, /angry, or /joy to name just a few and sure the animations were okay, but no matter what emote your character did, they had a blank look on his/her face.  <br /> <br />Glad SE added the little changes in detail too, along with big changes coming in the future.<div class="msgSig"><div class="msgSigBar sm">----------------------------</div><img src="http://common.zam.com/xivsigs/1758394.png" height="144" width="482" alt="Signature Image" border="0" /> <br /> <br />I'm the leader of Forest Federation and we are always recruiting! Our site link: forestfederation.guildportal.com</div></div>
